        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>façades [300002526], façades and façade components [300104722], exterior walls [300002523], walls by location or context [300002522], walls [300002469], walls and wall components [300052367], enclosing structural elements [300078050], structural elements [300078048], structural elements and components for structural elements [300078046], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
